Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}话题还很敏感\NKinda sensitive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你明白我的意思\NYou know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不会说的\NI don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想也是  你都经历过这么多事了\NI guess not, not after everything you've been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}吃饱了吗\NYou had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}饱了\NYes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好的\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}阿曼莎\NAmantha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}阿曼莎\NAmantha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们不应该...\NWe never should've...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不应该和委托人的妹妹有染\NI never should've gotten involved with
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-更别说...  -现在别做总结陈词\N- a client's sister, much less... - No summation now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拜托\Nplease.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们好啊\NWell, hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很久不见啊  阿曼莎\NLong time no see, Amantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我正减肥呢\NBeen watchin' my figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}效果不错\NWell, it shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们要点今日的推荐  自选三拼吗\NSo, ya'll want the meat and three special?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好\NUh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}给我来一块馅饼就好\NI'll just have a piece of pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么味道的\NWhat kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无所谓\NDoesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不会让你失望的\NI'll surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}太棒了\NGreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:18:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上帝  我真讨厌这小镇\NGod, I hate this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你真的不想挥上一杆吗\NSure you don't wanna hit a bucket?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我宁愿看你打\NI'd rather watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}随你便\NSuit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我老婆说我老爱管别人闲事\NYes, my wife says I'm nosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得我只是好奇心旺盛罢了\NI like to think of myself more as-as curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以  要是我不小心越界了\NSo, if I happen to cross some kind of imaginary line with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你得告诉我\Njust let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我哥们说\NSo, my buddies
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在死囚牢房的时候可以有配偶探监\Nsaid you could have conjugal visits on death row.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我跟他们说这都是扯淡  传闻而已\NI told 'em it was all BS, more like an urban legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有什么配偶探监\NThere are no conjugal visits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我就知道\NI knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你根本不能触碰别人  是吧\NYou couldn't even touch another person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不能接触\NNo touchin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那能把你搞神经了吧\NThat's gotta work on your psyche.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本来不会这样的\NYou weren't supposed to, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么叫本来\NWhat do you mean, wasn't supposed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我刚下狱那会儿  情况并非如此\NThings were a lot different when I was first incarcerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有些狱警缺乏监管\NA certain element of guards were less supervised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以发生了一些事\NSo, it, uh, created an environment for things to occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么...什么样的事\NThings... What-what, uh, what kinda things?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}应该说是遭遇吧\NEncounters, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}并非偶然  更像是某种开端\NWell, not by chance, more like an initiation of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}开端\NInitiation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可能因为他们在你脸上第一次看到类似乐观\NMaybe it was when they first saw somethin' akin to optimism
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或是平和的表情吧\Non your face, or a bit of peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或者当你开始自欺欺人地相信...\Nor just that moment when you began to believe that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你能在狱里安然无恙地生存\Nyou could survive it in some paradoxical way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道他们为什么那么做\NI don't know why they did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为其辩解就是一种滑坡谬误啊  小泰德\NJustification's a slippery slope, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}利用不合理的因果关系  以达到某种意欲之结论的逻辑谬误
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}某天早上  你动身去洗每周一次的淋浴\NSo, one mornin', you go off for your weekly shower,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一群狱友突然出现\Nand this group of inmates with particular compulsions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}态度特别蛮横\Nsuddenly appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你马上就会明白他们为何会来这儿\NYou understand at once why they're there,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可你就是无能为力\Nbut there's nothin' you can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你可以抗争  展现自己的男子气概\NYou can fight it, some symbolic gesture to your manhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但却无法阻止暴行\Nbut you can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}事情就那么发生了...\NSo, it happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一而再再而三\Nrepeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}见鬼\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后  结束了\NBut then, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们来也匆匆  去也匆匆\NJust as quickly as they appeared, they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这真是最怪异的事情了  小泰德\NIt's the strangest thing, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你又只身一人了\NThere you are, alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}水还在不停地流\NThe water's still runnin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}狱警又出现了  就像根本没离开过一样\NThe guards reappear like they never left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或许真的一直都在\NMaybe they didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我已经记不清了\NI don't know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后你洗完澡  穿好衣服\NSo, you finish your shower and get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}人还没回去  消息已经传开了\NWord gets back before you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}像样点儿的人不愿再拿正眼瞧你\NDecent guys on the row won't look at you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们为你感到难堪\NThey're too embarrassed for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有些人  当你经过他们的牢房\NThen, there are the ones who, when you pass by their cells,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们用最好奇的眼神盯着你  小泰德\Nthey look at you with the basest form of curiosity, Ted,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就好像你是畸形秀上的怪人\Nlike you were some freak show,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而他们要看个够\Nand they wanna get all their money's worth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别人的耻辱让他们尤为亢奋\Nbecause, more than anything, they're aroused by another shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你能明白吗\NYou know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}狱里还有一群特殊的人\NThen, there's a very special group on the row
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们看着你的眼神就好像...\Nwho look at you with this look, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我该怎么向你形容呢  小泰德\NHow can I describe it for ya, Ted,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎样你才能真正理解\Nso you can really understand it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好像他们可以把你拖进他们的牢房\NIt's like they can pull you into their cell
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不仅仅对你上下其手\Nand not just do things to ya,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而是真真正正地吃掉你\Nbut literally consume you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.30,0:21:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让你窒息\Ntake your breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}吞噬你的心\Neat your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}把你往死里糟蹋\Nand shit you out like you were nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这些事你可能无法想象\NI'm sure that was more than you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不过世间万事  很难判定\NBut, it is difficult to gauge things in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想  像你这样的人\NAnd like you, I suppose,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是很难掌握那些界限的\Nhard to know where the lines are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就这样...\NAnyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.89,0:22:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道它是怎么进来的\NI don't know how he got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你得对那小贱货采取点措施\NYou need to get that little son of a bitch some action.
