Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.28,0:32:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}丹尼尔  你最喜欢哪个季节\NDo you have, like, a-a favorite season, Daniel?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.50,0:32:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}最喜欢的季节吗\NA favorite season?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.60,0:32:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我个人很喜欢秋天\NPersonally, I like the fall a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.56,0:32:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我也非常喜爱仲夏的雨\NBut also, I love it when it rains on a hot summer day,
