Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.87,0:32:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}它能让我平静下来\Ncalms me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.69,0:32:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让植物也更有生气\NMakes the plants happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.85,0:32:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有打雷  我也很喜欢打雷\NAnd the thunder, I love the thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.99,0:33:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这让我想到上帝  并不是往坏的方向想\NIt makes me think of God, but not in a bad way.
