Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.71,0:33:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我意识到我脑海里想起的大多数事物\NI'm just so aware that most of what I draw on from inside my head
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.99,0:33:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都是源于我所读到的\Nare things I've read about.
