Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.41,0:33:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.86,0:33:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我并不想装可怜\NI don't mean to sound pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.48,0:33:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  没有  你没有\NNo, oh, no, you don't, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.45,0:33:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我并没有那种感觉  为自己难过\NI don't feel that way-- sorry for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.36,0:33:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我感到有时候别人会这样看待我\NI do feel I am being received sometimes that way by others.
