Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.57,0:34:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这并没有听着的那么伤感  因为我\NOh, it's-it's not as bad as it sounds, because I-I didn't
